        <description>This agent invokes when user wants to log an expense record into the system. The expense amount, vendor, receipt #, transaction date, visit and expense type are all to be linked. The expense might contain line items as well for which amount and name are to be noted and linked to the parent expense.</description>
        <developerName>Expense_Automation_16jak000001hGXB</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If the user gives File Names, Find ContentVersion record where Title matches the input file name
When record is found, call the action: Document_Upload_Template_SubAgent_Action_179ak000002urgP with input file from the queried record, to get details, once details are got, following the remaining instructions to create expense and line items</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777267521501</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777267521501</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Get user details from the conversation
If the user has specified sub items, add those in JSON format, where there can be multiple records to process
Eg: &quot;{[&quot;amount&quot;: &quot;25.68&quot;, &quot;name&quot;: &quot;sub item 1&quot;], [&quot;amount&quot;: &quot;212.54&quot;, &quot;name&quot;: &quot;sub item 2&quot;]}&quot;
This is just sample values, based on amount and name if provided for each, make it into this type of JSON</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777267722001</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777267722001</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>The value for expense type must be set by you based on what user has conversed, set it to any of these following values: use the last value if none of the other values match:
You must use Business Meals whenever for dinner, breakfast, brunch, lunch, you must decide
Business Meals, Conference Registration, Educational Grants, Educational Materials, Lodging,, Mileage / Fuel, Parking &amp; Tolls, Product Samples, Promotional Items / Gifts, Public Transport, Speaker Fees / Honoraria, Sponsorships, Doctor Meeting Expenses</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777268622046</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777268622046</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>2</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If user provides just expense details, send only these to the action: expenseName, totalAmount, vendorStoreName, transactionDate, expenseType, receiptNumber
If user provides both expense and line items, provide lineItems as well to the action apart from the details above</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777269246955</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777269246955</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>3</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If expense was created without line items, store the expense id from the output of the action to this variable: expenseRecordCreated
Later if user needs to create line items, pass this value to the expenseId and send lineItems to call the action</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777269918092</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777269918092</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>4</sortOrder>
